-= EHSM Ticket-System =-

Features needed:
	- create new ticket:
		- create printable ticket (LaTeX) with:
			barcode
			name
			logo
			conference dates and map on the back
		- add randomly generated barcode and name to database
	- validate a scanned barcode:
		- read barcode
		- query server with barcode
		- receive answer and give feedback

Concept:
	- client software interacts with barcode reader and asks server
	- server receives client requests and interacts with database

Constraints:
	- secure connection -> SSL

